            <thetext>Just checked that feature out. It&#39;s working good in the first place but as soon as you have opened some tabs and close all but not the last, the close icon is shown which makes the user think he can also close that tab. But as soon as he wants to close that, the button goes away.
Thats from a ser interface perspective not a good behavior because the UI looks like the user can close the tab and as soon as he tires, he can&#39;t anymore. So basically, we are fooling the user with such an UI.
Please take care of removing the icon as soon as the only one tab is shown.</thetext>
